        <h3>Presentation Mastery for Professionals</h3>
        <p><strong>Audience:</strong> Corporate Teams</p>
        <p><strong>Outcome:</strong> Effective slide decks, engaging delivery, and confident public speaking</p>
        <p><strong>Highlight:</strong> Multiple corporate teams received top feedback in internal presentations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- IMPACT -->
<section class="experience impact">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2>Our Impact</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>1,500+ learners trained across 3 years</li>
      <li>75+ workshops conducted nationally and online</li>
      <li>98% positive feedback from participants</li>
      <li>Hundreds of successful career transformations</li>
      <li>Corporate collaborations with leading organizations</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Interested in collaborating? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> with us and create impact together.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CALL TO ACTION -->
<section class="portfolio-cta">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2>Transform Your Communication Skills</h2>
    <p>
      Whether you are a student, professional, or organization, our programs are designed to help you excel in public speaking, presentations, and leadership communication. Join our community and become a confident, persuasive communicator.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta">Book a Consultation</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
